n of aam’s board” said dauch “my father’s vision passion and leadership have transformed aam into the leading global automotive supplier that it is today  i look forward to leading the aam board and the management team in executing our profitable growth plan while building value by delivering quality technology leadership and operational excellence for our customers around the world” dauch a member of the board of directors of aam since  has been serving as the company’s president and chief executive officer since september  since joining aam in july  he has served in positions of increasing responsibility including most recently president and chief operating officer full biographies and photos of mr dc dauch and mr tk walker are available at wwwaamcom automotive world is not responsible for the content of this news release  rachel boagey login remember me lost your password newsletter commercial vehicles electronics emobility manufacturing oems and markets powertrain safety suppliers quick links news analysis research data magazine webinars conferences megatrends magazine automotive megatrends magazine – q  june   conferences ghorpadi pune maharashtra india nov am  pmhd truck pune by automotive megatrendsthe westin pune koregaon park ghorpadi pune maharashtra india timetuesday  am   pm locationthe westin pune koregaon park ghorpadi pune maharashtra indiaghorpadi pune maharashtra india register now ghorpadi pune maharashtra india nov am  pmconnected car pune by automotive megatrendsthe westin pune koregaon park ghorpadi pune maharashtra india timewednesday  am   pm locationthe westin pune koregaon park ghorpadi pune maharashtra indiaghorpadi pune maharashtra india register now fairlane plaza  town center drive dearborn michigan  usa mar am  pmconnected car detroit by automotive megatrendsthe henry dearborn detroit timetuesday  am   pm locationthe henry dearborn detroitfairlane plaza  town center drive dearborn michigan  usa register now fairlane plaza  town center d